---
import { Image } from "astro:assets"
import Blueprint from "../images/blueprint.jpg"
---
<section class=" min-h-screen mt-20 text-white">

    <h2 class=" text-2xl text-center">Our Products</h2>

    <main class="py-12 md:px-20 sm:px-14 px-6">

        <div class="sm:flex items-center shadow-blue-400 shadow-md">

            <div class="md:px-10 sm:px-5">
              <h1 class="text-white font-bold text-2xl my-2">Long established</h1>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2 md:mb-6">We long established company that has supplied materials to various companines and construction sites. 
              </p>
            </div>

            <div>
                <Image loading="lazy" quality={"low"} src={Blueprint} alt="blueprint" />
            </div>

        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col space-y-2 lg:space-y-0 lg:flex-row items-stretch justify-center mt-10 lg:space-x-6  md:pt-10">

          <div class=" border border-gray-400 text-white text-3xl flex flex-col items-center justify-start space-y-6  rounded-3xl p-6 sm:min-h-[200px] w-full lg:w-1/3 hover:scale-105 hover:border-2 hover:border-blue-400 transition-transform duration-300 ease-in-out cursor-pointer">
                  <div class="flex flex-col space-y-2">
                      <span class=" text-left text-xl">Sand</span>
                      <span class=" text-gray-400 text-sm text-left">Meticulously sourced for purity and consistency, our sand is the essential building block for all your construction needs.</span>
                  </div>
          </div>

          <div class=" border border-gray-400 text-white text-3xl flex flex-col items-center justify-start space-y-6  rounded-3xl p-6 sm:min-h-[200px] w-full lg:w-1/3 hover:scale-105 hover:border-2 hover:border-blue-400 transition-transform duration-300 ease-in-out cursor-pointer">
                  <div class="flex flex-col space-y-2">
                      <span class=" text-left text-xl">Stones</span>
                      <span class=" text-gray-400 text-sm text-left">Whether you're crafting a beautiful landscape or fortifying a sturdy structure, our stones offer unmatched durability and timeless elegance.</span>
                  </div>
          </div>

          <div class=" border border-gray-400 text-white text-3xl flex flex-col items-center justify-start space-y-6  rounded-3xl p-6 sm:min-h-[200px] w-full lg:w-1/3 hover:scale-105 hover:border-2 hover:border-blue-400 transition-transform duration-300 ease-in-out cursor-pointer">
                  <div class="flex flex-col space-y-2">
                      <span class=" text-left text-xl">Ballast</span>
                      <span class=" text-gray-400 text-sm text-left">We offer premium ballast that is perfect for all your needs. Our ballast is sourced from the finest quarries, ensuring durability and reliability.</span>
                  </div>
          </div>
          
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col space-y-2 lg:space-y-0 lg:flex-row items-stretch justify-center mt-10 lg:space-x-6  md:pt-10">

          <div class=" border border-gray-400 text-white text-3xl flex flex-col items-center justify-start space-y-6  rounded-3xl p-6 sm:min-h-[200px] w-full lg:w-1/3 hover:scale-105 hover:border-2 hover:border-blue-400 transition-transform duration-300 ease-in-out cursor-pointer">
                  <div class="flex flex-col space-y-2">
                      <span class=" text-left text-xl">Cladding</span>
                      <span class=" text-gray-400 text-sm text-left">Elevate the aesthetics and durability of your building with our premium cladding materials.</span>
                  </div>
          </div>

          <div class=" border border-gray-400 text-white text-3xl flex flex-col items-center justify-start space-y-6  rounded-3xl p-6 sm:min-h-[200px] w-full lg:w-1/3 hover:scale-105 hover:border-2 hover:border-blue-400 transition-transform duration-300 ease-in-out cursor-pointer">
                  <div class="flex flex-col space-y-2">
                      <span class=" text-left text-xl">Steel Bars</span>
                      <span class=" text-gray-400 text-sm text-left">Our steel bars are engineered to provide unmatched tensile strength and durability, making them the ideal choice for reinforcing your structures.</span>
                  </div>
          </div>

          <div class="border border-gray-400 text-white text-3xl flex flex-col items-center justify-start space-y-6  rounded-3xl p-6 sm:min-h-[200px] w-full lg:w-1/3 hover:scale-105 hover:border-2 hover:border-blue-400 transition-transform duration-300 ease-in-out cursor-pointer">
                  <div class="flex flex-col space-y-2">
                      <span class=" text-left text-xl">Beams and Blocks</span>
                      <span class=" text-gray-400 text-sm text-left">Elevate your construction with our top-quality beams and blocks. Strong, durable, and easy to install.</span>
                  </div>
          </div>
          
        </div>

      </main>
</section>